# ====================
# Frontend - React/Vite/nginx
# ====================
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder
WORKDIR /app/frontend
COPY frontend/package*.json ./
RUN npm ci
COPY frontend/ ./
RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:alpine AS frontend
COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
COPY frontend/nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
EXPOSE 80
CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]

# ====================
# API - Go server
# ====================
FROM golang:1.22-alpine AS api-builder
WORKDIR /app/api
COPY api/go.mod api/go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY api/ ./
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -ldflags="-s -w" -o /server .

FROM alpine:3.19 AS api
RUN apk --no-cache add ca-certificates
COPY --from=api-builder /server /server
EXPOSE 8080
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s CMD wget -q --spider http://localhost:8080/healthz || exit 1
CMD ["/server"]

# ====================
# Worker - Python Celery
# ====================
FROM python:3.12-alpine AS worker-builder
WORKDIR /app/worker
COPY worker/requirements.txt ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --user -r requirements.txt

FROM python:3.12-alpine AS worker
WORKDIR /app/worker
COPY --from=worker-builder /root/.local /root/.local
ENV PATH=/root/.local/bin:$PATH
COPY worker/ ./
CMD ["celery", "-A", "app", "worker", "--loglevel=info"]
